Package bluemoose.mediator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AverageTimeResultInterface
    A mediator result containing the average time of something
    MacroTypeListResultInterface
    Mediator result for a list of all macro types in the system.
    MediatorInterface
    A mediator is responsible for handling requests made from a translator, in a manner independently of the translator, and routing requests to the correct data access component.
    MediatorResultInterface
    Base interface for all results returned by the mediator.
    ParameterExplanationResultInterface
    A response from the mediator containing a list of descriptions of parameters.
    StepListResultInterface
    Response from the mediator containing a list of driver steps.
    StoredMacroListResultInterface
    A response from the mediator containing a list of stored requests to run macros, or logged runs of macros.
